msgid ""
"This middleware obey :setting:`REDIRECT_MAX_TIMES` setting, :reqmeta:"
"`dont_redirect` and :reqmeta:`redirect_urls` request meta keys as described "
"for :class:`RedirectMiddleware`"
msgstr ""

